::SnowCat::

She looked at where the flier fell. She turned and looked at the 
other bot. "Check that one. I don't trust it." She moved in a little 
closer to the fallen bot, but keeping her distance.
"I think I'll be fine."  But she felt exhasuted and was very low on 
energy.
